title Side-panel layout state (current)

class PanelLayout {
  + left_collapsed : bool
  + right_collapsed : bool
  + sliver_width : f32
  + toggle_left() : void
  + toggle_right() : void
}

note bottom of PanelLayout
  Initialised with sliver_width = 18.0 (> 0). A collapsed
  panel is rebuilt as a SidePanel.exact_width(sliver_width)
  whose whole area is an expand button, so it can always
  be brought back (OCL-PANEL-SLIVER-MIN).
end note
